{"tid":396926,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"公開信稱院長為「黃乃共」　新亞學生會解釋出於手誤","createTime":"2017-09-12T05:18:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T05:42:27.000Z","uid":18348,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"496bc938cdd01984c4807be11f0baa90b81f05db","tid":396926,"uid":18348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1353587_1_L_20170912102458.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1353587_1_L_20170912102458.jpg&h=307cb334&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中大學生會早前發公開信回應新亞書院院長黃乃正時，上款稱他為「黃乃共」，中大新亞書院學生會幹事方潔儀在本台節目中解釋，是出於手誤，他們事後已發出更正版本，但按慣例仍然保留舊版。<br />\n<br />\n她在節目後表示，已主動約見黃乃正明日會面，學生會將再討論如何處理事件，她說，往後在發稿前會謹慎審閱稿件。<br />\n<br />\n新亞書院校董會副主席陳志新在本台節目上提到，對事件感到遺憾，認為邏輯上不能接受，期望學生會誠心道歉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1353587-20170912.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1353587-20170912.htm&d=Zr%2BVOBPEarKjkVeetHidjJUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=ea6c244a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1353587-20170912.htm&h=da5bc728\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1353587-20170912.htm</a>"},{"pid":"2a80cc580d2476d43ae7cb345a139453b38ba35b","tid":396926,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:19:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ad7e2acd1aad3d66c6260fb7a12a73a2d8455fe","tid":396926,"uid":37196,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:20:44.000Z","msg":"院長寫錯就得<br />\n學生唔可以寫錯?<br />\n<br />\n道歉你又話唔誠心，你講撚晒啦"},{"pid":"9cb1d446a7b271f732453aa10abc5a0fd9411609","tid":396926,"uid":116289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T05:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\"